<li id="cite_note-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6" title="">^</a></b> Interview with Amit Goswami by Conny Hill, New Connexion, September 2002 <a href="http://www.newconnexion.net/article/09-02/goswami.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.newconnexion.net/article/09-02/goswami.html" rel="nofollow">[5]</a></li>
